Raymond C. Pecor III

Age : 48Public asset : 1,034,199 USDLinked companies :  Community Bank System, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Raymond C. Pecor, III, is President at Lake Champlain Transportation Co.He is on the Board of Directors at Community Bank System, Inc., Community Bank, NA (Summersville, Missouri), Merchants Bank, Inc. (Burlington, Vermont), Champlain College and The Champlain Valley Exposition. Mr. Pecor was previously employed as an Independent Director by Merchants Bancshares, Inc.



